description: Exsitec Holding AB provides information technology systems and solutions. The company is headquartered in Linkoping, Ostergotland and currently employs 263 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-09-16. The firm was founded in 2000 and is located in Linkoping, Sweden. The company specializes in digitizing the operations of small and medium-sized companies with the help of business systems, decision support and tailored business applications. The firm is a reseller of software in areas such as business systems, decision support, electronic invoice management and CRM.
name: Exsitec Holding AB
